headline: Can Jabil’s (JBL) AI Security Push Reinforce Its Edge in Data Center Infrastructure?
summary: Earlier this week, Axiado Corporation announced a collaboration with Jabil Inc. to deliver AI-driven cybersecurity and Open Compute Project modular server solutions, with both companies showcasing their technologies at the OCP Global Summit in San Jose. This partnership highlights Jabil’s push into next-generation AI and cloud data center infrastructure, expanding its footprint in a sector that is experiencing rapid technological change and customer demand.
